api_list.name: Color Format
api_list.description: Get a color format guess based on the string passed.

required_parameters.name: value
required_parameters.description: Any color string. Some color formats use the same notation, and the API will guess the composition of the input string. As an example, if you pass the string "135°, 96%, 39%" it could be an HSV or HSL color. The API will assume HSL in this case.

api_list.code:

url = "https://convert-colors.p.rapidapi.com/format/135°, 96%, 39%"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "convert-colors.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
api_list.convert_code:
